ing%20to%20declassify%20files%20about%20aliens%20and%20UFOs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat%20could%20mean%20huge%20payouts%20for%20traders%20betting%20on%20alien%20disclosure%20on%20the%20prediction%20platform%20Polymarket.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAliens%20have%20long%20occupied%20a%20strange%20but%20persistent%20corner%20of%20the%20betting%20world.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20says%20he%20is%20directing%20federal%20agencies%20to%20declassify%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fufo-sightings-ratcliffe-new-report-intel-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUFO%20files%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20traders%20betting%20on%20aliens%2C%20that%20could%20mean%20a%20very%20earthly%20payday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20the%20tremendous%20interest%20shown%2C%20I%20will%20be%20directing%20the%20Secretary%20of%20War%2C%20and%20other%20relevant%20Departments%20and%20Agencies%2C%20to%20begin%20the%20process%20of%20identifying%20and%20releasing%20Government%20files%20related%20to%20alien%20and%20extraterrestrial%20life%2C%20unidentified%20aerial%20phenomena%20(UAP)%2C%20and%20unidentified%20flying%20objects%20(UFOs)%2C%20and%20any%20and%20all%20other%20information%20connected%20to%20these%20highly%20complex%2C%20but%20extremely%20interesting%20and%20important%2C%20matters%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20in%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post%20on%20Thursday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Trump%20took%20aim%20at%20former%20President%20Barack%20Obama%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20improperly%20discussing%20classified%20material%20when%20speaking%20about%20extraterrestrial%20life%20on%20a%20recent%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20told%20reporters%20aboard%20Air%20Force%20One%20that%20Obama%20%26quot%3Bgave%20classified%20information%26quot%3B%20and%20wasn't%20%26quot%3Bsupposed%20to%20be%20doing%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20he%20could%20get%20him%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20trouble%26quot%3B%20by%20declassifying%20the%20relevan