%20Waymo%20autonomous%20self-driving%20Jaguar%20electric%20vehicle%20wrapped%20with%20a%20football%20graphic%20is%20seen%20navigating%20a%20roadblock%20during%20NFL%20Super%20Bowl%20weekend%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20California%20on%20February%207%2C%202026.%20(Photo%20by%20Patrick%20T.%20Fallon%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6997c02df8731049f3af7356%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222125%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWaymo's%20NY%20robotaxi%20plan%20falls%20through%20after%20Gov.%20Hochul%20drops%20proposal%20to%20legalize%20unsupervised%20robotaxis.%3Cp%3EPatrick%20T.%20Fallon%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWaymo's%20New%20York%20robotaxi%20dreams%20are%20on%20hold%20as%20Gov.%20Kathy%20Hochul%20drops%20an%20uncrewed%20robotaxi%20proposal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20proposal%20would%20have%20allowed%20robotaxis%20to%20run%20outside%20NYC%2C%20with%20local%20government%20approval.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20blow%20came%20days%20after%20Waymo%20raised%20%2416%20billion%20to%20fund%20plans%20to%20expand%20to%2020%20more%20cities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20autonomous%20vehicle%20industry%20just%20faced%20a%20setback%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20Gov.%20Kathy%20Hochul%20dropped%20a%20proposal%20to%20allow%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-robotaxi-depot-san-francisco-what-does-it-look-like-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erobotaxi%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20operate%20commercially%20without%20human%20safety%20drivers%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20state%20outside%20New%20York%20City%2C%20dealing%20a%20blow%20not%20just%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-robotaxi-depot-san-francisco-what-does-it-look-like-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWaymo%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20also%20to%20its%20competitors%20eager%20to%20crack%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20taxi%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%2C%20which%20Hochul%20introduced%20last%20month%20as%20part%20of%20her%20budget%20plan%2C%20would%20have%20created%20a%20framework%20for%20limited%20robotaxi%20deployments%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20state%20while%20leaving%20any%20decision%20about%20New%20York%20City%20to%20the%20mayor%20and%20city%20council.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20proposal%2C%20private%20companies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-vs-waymo-robotaxi-autonomous-self-driving-test-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWaymo%20and%20Tesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20be%20able%20to%20operate%20their%20commercial%20robotaxis%20if%20they%20could%20obtain%20approval%20from%20local%20governments.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20the%20governor's%20office%20confirmed%20that%20the%20plan%20had%20been%20withdrawn%20after%20failing%20to%20gain%20legislative%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20is%20a%20blow%20to%20Waymo%2C%20which%20has%20eyed%20New%20York%2C%20especially%20New%20York%20City%2C%20for%20years%20as%20a%20potential%20growth%20market.%20Waymo%20is%20currently%20testing%20vehicles%20with%20safety%20drivers%20in%20New%20York%20City%20under%20a%20permit%20approved%20during%20former%20Mayor%20Eric%20Adams'%20administration%2C%20though%20that%20permit%20expires%20March%2031.%20It%20is%20unclear%20if%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzohran-mamdani-proposals-how-much-they-will-cost-affordability-childcare-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMayor%20Zohran%20Mamdani%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20agree%20to%20renew%20the%20permit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20blog%20post%20on%20Monday%2C%20Waymo%20said%20it%20raised%20%2416%20billion%20in%20its%20most%20recent%20funding%20round%2C%20which%20valued%20the%20company%20at%20%24126%20billion.%20The%20investment%20would%20be%20used%20to%20finance%20the%20company's%20expansion%20to%20over%2020%20more%20cities%2C%20said%20Waymo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20state%20lobbying%20records%2C%20the%20Alphabet-owned%20company%20has%20been%20lobbying%20Hochul%2C%20state%20senators%2C%20state%20assembly%20members%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Blake%20Washington%2C%20who%20is%20the%20state's%20budget%20director%2C%20over%20the%20past%20six%20months.%20Other%20companies%20that%20are%20developing%20robotaxis%20don't%20have%20notable%20lobbying%20records%20specific%20to%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20law%20allows%20autonomous%20vehicles%20only%20if%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-tesla-robotaxi-camera-vision-lidar-debate-human-comparison-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehuman%20safety%20driver%3C%2Fa%3E%20keeps%20their%20hands%20on%20the%20steering%20wheel.%20Earlier%20versions%20of%20the%20law%20even%20required%20a%20police%20escort%2C%20but%20that%20provision%20was%20later%20removed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAutonomous%20vehicle%20makers%20have%20struggled%20to%20gain%20a%20foothold%20in%20New%20York.%20Cruise%20shelved%20plans%20to%20test%20in%20Manhattan%20in%202017%20before%20the%20company%20folded%20entirely%2C%20while%20Optimus%20Ride%20and%20Mobileye%20have%20run%20limited%20pilots.%20None%20has%20thus%20far%20managed%20to%20provide%20unsupervised%20commercial%20rides%20in%20the%20Big%20Apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20active%20bills%20that%20would%20allow%20robotaxis%20to%20run%20in%20the%20state%20if%20such%20plans%20could%20gain%20enough%20legislative%20support.%20Brian%20A.%20Cunningham%2C%20who%20represents%20the%2043rd%20Assembly%20District%20in%20Central%20Brooklyn%2C%20has%20sponsored%20a%20bill%20that%20would%20allow%20a%20person%20or%20a%20company%20to%20operate%20a%20fully%20autonomous%20vehicle%20on%20the%20public%20roads%20without%20a%20human%20driver%2C%20%26quot%3Bprovided%20that%20the%20automated%20driving%20system%20is%20engaged%20and%20the%20vehicle%20meets%20certain%20conditions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20in%20question%20was%20first%20referred%20to%20the%20Committee%20of%20Transportation%20on%20January%207.%20Based%20on%20state%20lobbying%20records%2C%20Waymo%20lobbyists%20met%20with%20Cunningham%20between%20November%20and%20December%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaymo%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fny-scraps-plan-to-legalize-driverless-robotaxis-blow-to-waymo-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771562773000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6997c514f8731049f3af7386%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fny-scraps-plan-to-legalize-driverless-robotaxis-blow-to-waymo-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22New%20York's%20governor%20dropped%20a%20proposal%20to%20allow%20unmanned%20robotaxis%2C%20days%20after%20Waymo%20raised%20%2416%20billion%20to%20fund%20its%20expansion%20to%20more%20cities%20in%20the%20US.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22katherineli%40insider.com%20(Katherine%20Li)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fny-scraps-plan-to-legalize-driverless-robotaxis-blow-to-waymo-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Daniel%20Radcliffe%20reveals%20what%20almost%20ended%20his%20life%20while%20filming%20%E2%80%98Harry%20Potter%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771562740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-128591361%2Cimgsize-20724.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fdaniel-radcliffe-shares-that-he-almost-drowned-while-filming-this-scene-from-the-harry-potter-films%2Farticleshow%2F128591361.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.india