f9955cef11a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221767%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESam%20Altman%3Cp%3EFlorian%20Gaertner%2FPhotothek%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20is%20offering%20resources%20to%20staff%20who%20may%20be%20navigating%20ICE%20detention%20or%20Border%20Patrol%20inspections.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20new%20resources%20include%20%2415%2C000%20of%20reimbursed%20legal%20fees%20and%20referrals%20to%20immigration%20counsel.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20resource%20package%20comes%20shortly%20after%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20said%20ICE%20%26quot%3Bis%20going%20too%20far.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20is%20rolling%20out%20a%20new%20package%20of%20resources%20for%20employees%20who%20may%20be%20navigating%20interactions%20with%20US%20immigration%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20is%20designed%20to%20help%20staff%20directly%20affected%20by%20Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20(ICE)%20detention%20or%20prolonged%20secondary%20inspection%20by%20US%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20(CBP)%20%E2%80%94%20including%20situations%20involving%20an%20employee%20or%20an%20immediate%20family%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20comes%20as%20the%20nation%20grapples%20with%20fallout%20from%20a%20series%20of%20federal%20immigration%20enforcement%20incidents%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fice-shooting-minneapolis-alex-pretti-business-tech-leaders-react-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elethal%20shootings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20have%20triggered%20widespread%20protests%20and%20corporate%20pushback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20OpenAI%20spokesperson%2C%20the%20support%20resources%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUp%20to%20%2415%2C000%20(gross)%20in%20reimbursement%20for%20approved%20expenses%20tied%20to%20immigration%20detention%20or%20enforcement%20interactions%2C%20such%20as%20immigration%20legal%20services%2C%20meals%2C%20lodging%2C%20and%20transportation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExpedited%20referrals%20to%20external%20immigration%20counsel.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20resource%20guide%20for%20handling%20complex%20immigration%20situations%2C%20including%20guidance%20on%20locating%20detained%20individuals%20and%20referrals%20to%20low-cost%20or%20pro%20bono%20counsel.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20regularly%20review%20our%20employee%20benefits%20to%20ensure%20they%20reflect%20the%20needs%20of%20our%20workforce%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAs%20part%20of%20that%20process%2C%20we%20updated%20our%20support%20resources%20for%20employees%20facing%20complex%20immigration-related%20situations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%2C%20which%20relies%20on%20skilled%20workers%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%20declined%20to%20specify%20how%20many%20employees%20might%20require%20the%20use%20of%20the%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20follows%20internal%20conversations%20at%20OpenAI%20about%20federal%20immigration%20enforcement%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-parent-sam-altman-proudest-accomplishment-no-longer-openai-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECEO%20Sam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E's%20recent%20message%20to%20employees%20criticizing%20ICE's%20actions%20as%20going%20%26quot%3Btoo%20far.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20previously%20reported%20that%20in%20a%20late%20January%20internal%20Slack%20message%2C%20Altman%20expressed%20concern%20about%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-ice-minnesota-shooting-response-slack-message-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eimmigration%20enforcement%20activity%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sparking%20strong%20reactions%20within%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman's%20comments%20came%20amid%20heightened%20national%20scrutiny%20over%20ICE%20and%20Border%20Patrol%20operations%2