20you%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20generally%202%20types%20of%20LLM%20users%2C%20those%20that%20use%20it%20to%20learn%20everything%20%2C%20and%20those%20that%20use%20it%20so%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20learn%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Cuban%20said%20of%20large%20language%20models%20in%20an%20X%20post%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BShark%20Tank%26quot%3B%20billionaire%20has%20been%20bullish%20about%20AI%20and%20said%20that%20companies%20need%20to%20embrace%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuban%20has%20said%20there%20will%20be%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-ai-artificial-intelligence-comments-chatgpt-openai-google-microsoft-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etwo%20types%20of%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20those%20who%20are%20great%20at%20AI%2C%20and%20everybody%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20Business%20Insider's%20James%20Faris%20previously%20reported.%20He's%20also%20said%20that%20AI%20models%20can't%20provide%20all%20the%20answers%20and%20are%20%26quot%3Bstupid%26quot%3B%20but%20like%20%26quot%3Ba%20savant%20that%20remembers%20everything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBill%20Gurley%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20venture%20capitalist%20firm%20Benchmark%2C%20agrees%20%26quot%3B100%25%26quot%3B%20with%20Cuban%20that%20there%20are%20two%20types%20of%20AI%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20on%20a%20custom%20career%20path%20where%20you%20aim%20to%20differentiate%20yourself%2C%20AI%20is%20'jet%20fuel'%20-%20you%20can%20learn%20and%20soar%20faster%20than%20ever%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20Gurley%20said%20on%20X%20in%20response%20to%20Cuban.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%2C%20it%20could%20have%20the%20opposite%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20some%20of%20AI's%20biggest%20proponents%20have%20warned%20that%20the%20technology%20could%20make%20people%20lazy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistral-ai-ceo-risk-ai-lazy-deskilling-dario-amodei-jobs-2025-6%5C%2