itle%22%3A%22Meta's%20metaverse%20is%20going%20mobile%20%E2%80%94%20and%20leaving%20VR%20behind%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mark%20Zuckerberg%20wearing%20a%20VR%20headset%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6997a36ce1ba468a96ac5b85%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeta%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20wears%20a%20virtual%20reality%20headset%3Cp%3Ecredit%20should%20read%20GLENN%20CHAPMAN%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%20is%20shifting%20Horizon%20Worlds'%20focus%20from%20VR%20to%20a%20mobile%20app.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMeta's%20Reality%20Labs%2C%20which%20has%20lost%20nearly%20%2480%20billion%20since%202020%2C%20sees%20mobile%20as%20a%20key%20growth%20area.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%20faces%20competition%20from%20Roblox%20and%20Fortnite%20in%20the%20mobile%20gaming%20market%20with%20Horizon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20is%20dialing%20back%20the%20metaverse%20to%20mean%20something%20far%20less%20futuristic%3A%20an%20app%20on%20your%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%2C%20which%20spent%20billions%20of%20dollars%20to%20build%20Horizon%20Worlds%20%E2%80%94%20an%20immersive%2C%20virtual%20hangout%20zone%20on%20its%20Quest%20virtual%20reality%20headsets%20%E2%80%94%20is%20%26quot%3Bshifting%20focus%26quot%3B%20for%20Horizon%20Worlds%20%26quot%3Bto%20be%20almost%20exclusively%20mobile%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20blog%20post%20published%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHorizon%20Worlds%20is%20part%20of%20Meta's%20Reality%20Labs%20division%20for%20VR%20products%20and%20smart%20glasses%2C%20a%20unit%20that%20has%20burned%20nearly%20%2480%20billion%20since%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLast%20year%2C%20we%20began%20to%20experiment%20with%20Worlds%20as%20a%20mobile%20platform%2C%20and%20we%20saw%20positive%20momentum%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Samantha%20Ryan%2C%20Meta's%20vice%20president%20of%20content%20at%20Reality%20Labs.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20to%20truly%20change%20the%20game%20and%20tap%20into%20a%20much%20larger%20market%2C%20we're%20going%20all-in%20on%20mobile.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20signals%20how%20dramatically%20Meta%20has%20redrawn%20its%20VR%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-layoffs-reality-labs-vr-horizon-worlds-teams-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%20laid%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%20roughly%2010%25%20of%20Reality%20Labs%20employees%2C%20closed%20three%20VR%20gaming%20studios%20it%20owned%2C%20and%20stopped%20releasing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzuckerberg-meta-layoffs-vr-supernatural-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enew%20content%20for%20Supernatural%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20popular%20VR%20fitness%20app%20it%20acquired%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20said%20it%20is%20still%20committed%20to%20virtual%20reality%20hardware%20and%20supporting%20third-party%20developers%20who%20create%20games%20for%20it.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20in%20it%20for%20the%20long%20haul%2C%26quot%3B%20Ryan%20wrote%2C%20and%20pointed%20to%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3Brobust%20roadmap%20of%20future%20VR%20headsets%20tailored%20to%20different%20audience%20segments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20invested%20nearly%20%24150%20million%20in%20VR%20developer%20platforms%20in%202025%2C%20Ryan%20wrote%2C%20and%20she%20said%20that%20popular%20games%20like%20%26quot%3BThe%20Thrill%20of%20the%20Fight%202%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BHard%20Bullet%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BUG%26quot%3B%20had%20earned%20%26quot%3Bmillions%26quot%3B%20in%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20she%20wrote%20that%2086%25%20of%20the%20time%20people%20spend%20in%20Meta's%20headsets%20is%20in%20third-party%20apps%2C%20not%20its%20own.%20The%20pivot%20to%20mobile%20effectively%20pits%20Horizon%20Worlds%20against%20entrenched%20competitors%20like%20Rob