al%20Family%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20decided%2C%20as%20I%20always%20have%2C%20to%20put%20my%20duty%20to%20my%20family%20and%20country%20first.%20I%20stand%20by%20my%20decision%20five%20years%20ago%20to%20stand%20back%20from%20public%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20His%20Majesty's%20agreement%2C%20we%20feel%20I%20must%20now%20go%20a%20step%20further%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20went%20on%20to%20say.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20therefore%20no%20longer%20use%20my%20title%20or%20the%20honours%20which%20have%20been%20conferred%20upon%20me.%20As%20I%20have%20said%20previously%2C%20I%20vigorously%20deny%20the%20accusations%20against%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20royal%20stopped%20being%20known%20as%20Prince%20Andrew%20after%20the%20announcement%2C%20going%20by%20Andrew%20Mountbatten-Windsor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJanuary%202026%3A%20The%20Department%20of%20Justice%20released%20more%20Epstein%20files%2C%20including%20photos%20of%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20appearing%20to%20kneel%20over%20an%20unidentified%20woman.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221862%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Prince%20Andrew%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6997401da645d118818999ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221397%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPrince%20Andrew%20has%20lost%20his%20royal%20titles%20following%20scandals%20involving%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20and%20an%20alleged%20Chinese%20spy.%3Cp%3EMax%20Mumby%2FIndigo%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20January%2030%2C%202026%2C%20drop%20of%20Epstein%20files%20included%20photos%20of%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20appearing%20to%20kneel%20over%20an%20unidentified%20woman%2C%20who%20was%20clothed%20and%20lying%20on%20the%20floor.%20It's%20unclear%20when%20or%20where%20the%20photos%20were%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20files%20also%20include%20emails%20between%20Epstein%20and%20an%20account%20called%20%26quot%3BThe%20Duke%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20signs%20his%20emails%20%26quot%3BA%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20well%20as%20exchanges%20between%20Epstein%20and%20Ferguson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFebruary%202026%3A%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20was%20arrested%20on%20suspicion%20of%20misconduct%20in%20public%20office.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Andrew%20Mountbatten%20Windsor%20leaves%20Aylsham%20Police%20Station%20the%20same%20day%20he%20was%20arrested%20on%20suspicion%20of%20misconduct%20in%20public%20office%20in%20February%202026.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69977404f8731049f3af6e52%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222286%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndrew%20Mountbatten%20Windsor%20leaves%20Aylsham%20Police%20Station%20the%20same%20day%20he%20was%20arrested%20on%20suspicion%20of%20misconduct%20in%20public%20office%20in%20February%202026.%3Cp%3EPhil%20Noble%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrew-mountbatten-windsor-arrested-suspicion-misconduct-public-office-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Earrested%20on%20suspicion%20of%20misconduct%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20public%20office.%20It%20was%20his%2066th%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20prince%20served%20as%20UK%20trade%20envoy%20from%202001%20to%202011%2C%20and%20the%20Epstein%20files%20appear%20to%20show%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20forwarding%20emails%20with%20his%20official%20work%20reports%20to%20the%20disgraced%20financier%20in%202010%20and%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFollowing%20a%20thorough%20assessment%2C%20we%20have%20now%20opened%20an%20investigation%20into%20this%20allegation%20of%20misconduct%20in%20public%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20Oliver%20Wright%2C%20the%20assistant%20chief%20constable%20with%20the%20Thames%20Valley%20Police%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20important%20that%20we%20protect%20the%20integrity%20and%20objectivity%20of%20our%20investigation%20as%20we%20work%20with%20our%20partners%20to%20investigate%20this%20alleged%20offence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKing%20Charles%20released%20a%20statement%20about%20the%20arrest%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20learned%20with%20the%20deepest%20concern%20the%20news%20about%20Andrew%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20and%20suspicion%20of%20misconduct%20in%20public%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20now%20follows%20is%20the%20full%2C%20fair%2C%20and%20proper%20process%20by%20which%20this%20issue%20is%20investigated%20in%20the%20appropriate%20manner%20and%20by%20the%20appropriate%20authorities.%20In%20this%2C%20as%20I%20have%20said%20before%2C%20they%20have%20our%20full%20and%20wholehearted%20support%20and%20co-operation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20me%20state%20clearly%3A%20the%20law%20must%20take%20its%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20king's%20statement%20went%20on%20to%20say.%20%26quot%3BAs%20this%20process%20continues%2C%20it%20would%20not%20be%20right%20for%20me%20to%20comment%20further%20on%20this%20matter.%20Meanwhile%2C%20my%20family%20and%20I%20will%20continue%20in%20our%20duty%20and%20service%20to%20you%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20were%20photographed%20at%20Sandringham%20estate%20in%20Norfolk%2C%20where%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20had%20been%20living%2C%20as%20well%20as%20his%20previous%20residence%20in%20Berkshire%2C%20on%20Thursday%2C%20carrying%20out%20searches%20of%20the%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20released%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20%26quot%3Bunder%20investigation%26quot%3B%20around%2011%20hours%20after%20his%20arrest%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fbritain-epstein-andrew-former-prince-arrested-fb0b9e738bf7ede10651914ee3f3583d%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAP%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20was%20photographed%20leaving%20the%20Aylsham%20Police%20Station%20in%20a%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprince-andrew-jeffrey-epstein-timeline-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771539376000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699743f8a645d11881899a65%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprince-andrew-jeffrey-epstein-timeline-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Andrew%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20was%20arrested%20on%20Thursday%20on%20suspicion%20of%20misconduct%20in%20public%20office.%20Here's%20a%20timeline%20of%20his%20ties%20to%20Jeffrey%20Epstein.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfriel%40businessinsider.com%20(Mikhaila%20Friel%2CSamantha%20Grindell%20Pettyjohn)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprince-andrew-jeffrey-epstein-timeline-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%2011%20best%20petite%20clothing%20brands%20that%20that%20saved%20me%20from%20constant%20tailoring%20appointments%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20side-by-side%20photos%20of%20a%20petite%20woman%20modeling%20different%20outfits%3A%20on%20the%20left%2C%20a%20casual%20fall%20look%20with%20a%20denim%20shirt%2C%20straight-leg%20jeans%2C%20brown%20knit%20vest%2C%20and%20loafers%20outdoors%3B%20in%20the%20center%2C%20a%20white%20sleeveless%20midi%20dress%20styled%20for%20a%20dressier%20occasion%3B%20on%20the%20right%2C%20a%20tailored%20brown%20blazer%20and%20matching%20mini%20skirt%20paired%20with%20a%20white%20turtleneck%2C%20shown%20in%20a%20mirror%20selfie.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69977700f8731049f3af6edd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2C%20Rebecca%20Strong%2C%20Samantha%20Crozier%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFinding%20clothing%20that%20fits%20flawlessly%20has%20never%20been%20easy%20for%20me.%20Tops%20slide%20off%20my%20narrow%20shoulders%20or%20bunch%20at%20the%20wrists%2C%20and%20jeans%20and%20trousers%20almost%20always%20need%20hemming%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%205-foot-3%2C%20after%20all.%20Fortunately%20for%20me%20(and%20all%20the%20other%20shorties%20out%20there)%2C%20plenty%20of%20brands%20now%20offer%20petite%20lines%20designed%20specifically%20for%20frames%20like%20mine%20%E2%80%94%20no%20expensive%20alterations%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20petite%2C%20you%20probably%20know%20the%20struggle.%20Standard%20tops%20and%20dresses%20can%20feel%20boxy%2C%20sleeves%20look%20cartoonishly%20long%2C%20waistlines%20and%20knee%20breaks%20hit%20too%20low%2C%20and%20pants%20bunch%20awkwardly%20at%20the%20crotch%20or%20drag%20on%20the%20ground.%20I%20used%20to%20joke%20that%20I%20looked%20like%20a%20kid%20who%20raided%20her%20mom's%20closet.%20While%20petite%20clothing%20is%20generally%20made%20for%20people%205-foot-4%20and%20under%2C%20it's%20not%20just%20about%20shorter%20inseams%20and%20hemlines.%20The%20best%20pieces%20also%20include%20thoughtful%20proportion%20adjustments%20%E2%80%94%20like%20shorter%20rises%2C%20scaled-down%20sleeves%2C%20and%20higher%2C%20smaller%20armholes%20that%20keep%20your%20bra%20from%20peeking%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20genuinely%20thrilled%20to%20see%20more%20brands%20expand%20their%20petite%20offerings%2C%20and%20I've%20tested%20nearly%20every%20one%20I%20can%20find.%20Below%20are%20the%20petite%20clothing%20brands%20that%20truly%20stand%20out%20for%20their%20quality%2C%20fit%2C%20and%20versatility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20overall%3A%20Petite%20Studio%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22original%20photo%20of%20the%20editor%20in%20petite%20studio%2C%20next%20to%20a%20photo%20of%20the%20model%20in%20petite%20studio%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699774dcf8731049f3af6e75%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Crozier%2FBusiness%20Insider%2C%20Petite%20Studio%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20tons%20of%20retailers%20that%20have%20a%20petite%20section.%20But%20lots%20of%20times%2C%20these%20are%20full%20of%20standard-sized%20garments%20that%20are%20simply%20shortened%20%E2%80%94%20which%20means%20you're%20getting%20garments%20that%20will%20be%20the%20right%20length%2C%20but%20aren't%20necessarily%20tailored%20to%20fit%20the%20petite%20body.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fredirect.viglink.com%2F%3Fu%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.petitestudionyc.com%252F%26key%3Da0a489b80c119e1fb25b8b4606294f7e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPetite%20Studio%20%3C%2Fa%3Esolves%20this%20problem%20by%20fitting%20all%20of%20their%20garments%20on%20real%20petite%20fit%20models%2C%20so%20they're%20designed%20from%20start%20to%20finish%20for%20short%20folks.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20absolutely%20tell%20the%20difference.%20I've%20tried%20all%20the%20tricks%20for%20buying%20clothing%2C%20like%20looking%20for%20cropped%20cuts%20or%20hemming%20standard%20sized%20bottoms%2C%20but%20nothing%20fits%20better%20than%20a%20piece%20that%20was%20designed%20especially%20for%20someone%20my%20height.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20huge%20fan%20of%20the%20brand's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fredirect.viglink.com%2F%3Fu%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.petitestudionyc.com%252Fcollections%252Fcoats-jackets%26key%3Da0a489b80c119e1fb25b8b4606294f7e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eouterwear%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20are%20tons%20of%20trendy%20coats%20that%20have%20been%20designed%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20finesse%20to%20b