0you're%20on%20the%20shorter%20side%20(5-foot-1%20and%20under)%20or%20you're%20buying%20ankle%20length%20pants%20or%20jeans%2C%2025%20inches%20may%20be%20a%20better%20bet%20%E2%80%94%20whereas%20if%20you're%20closer%20to%205-foot-4%20or%20plan%20to%20wear%20heels%2C%20you%20might%20opt%20for%20a%2028%20inch%20inseam.%20A%20mid-rise%20is%20the%20most%20universally%20flattering%20and%20versatile%2C%20because%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20it%20hitting%20at%20an%20awkward%20place%20on%20your%20shorter%20torso.%20That%20said%2C%20as%20long%20as%20you're%20buying%20a%20petite-specific%20piece%2C%20you%20can%20rest%20assured%20that%20even%20high-rise%20and%20low-rise%20options%20have%20been%20adjusted%20to%20accommodate%20the%20proportions%20of%20your%20frame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETorso%20length%20is%20worth%20considering%2C%20too%3A%20Petite-sized%20tops%20and%20dresses%20are%20generally%20designed%20with%20higher%20waistlines%20and%20raised%20hems%2C%20but%20knowing%20your%20exact%20measurements%20can%20help%20you%20select%20styles%20that%20are%20more%20appropriate%20for%20your%20body.%20For%20instance%2C%20long%2C%20tunic%20style%20tops%20may%20not%20work%20for%20those%20with%20particularly%20short%20torsos%20%E2%80%94%20even%20in%20petite%20sizing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EKnow%20when%20hemming%20makes%20sense%20and%20when%20it%20doesn't.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20all%20you%20need%20is%20a%20good%20tailor%20to%20make%20a%20piece%20of%20clothing%20fit%20your%20petite%20frame%20flawlessly.%20Assuming%20that%20the%20only%20fit%20issue%20is%20that%20a%20piece%20is%20too%20long%2C%20hemming%20makes%20sense%20for%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EStraight-leg%2Fskinny%20pants%20and%20jeans%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShift%20dresses%2C%20sheath%20dresses%2C%20and%20other%20simple%20silhouette%20dresses%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStraight%20miniskirts%20and%20midi%20skirts%2C%20as%20well%20as%20pencil%20skirts%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20taking%20up%20certain%20styles%20at%20the%20hem%20%E2%80%94%20like%20flared%20and%20boot-cut%20jeans%2C%20structured%20wide-leg%20trousers%2C%20dresses%20with%20belts%20or%20multiple%20ruffled%20tiers%2C%20and%20A-line%20dresses%20%E2%80%94%20can%20throw%20off%20the%20overall%20proportions.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20flare%20might%20not%20start%20at%20the%20right%20spot%20on%20the%20leg%2C%20or%20the%20belt%20on%20the%20dress%20might%20not%20sit%20at%20the%20natural%20waist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EUse%20tricks%20when%20there%20is%20no%20petite%20sizing.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20because%20you're%20petite%20doesn't%20necessarily%20mean%20you%20%3Cem%3Ehave%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20wear%20clothes%20that%20are%20specially%20designed%20for%20petite%20frames.%20If%20your%20favorite%20brands%20don't%20have%20petite%20lines%2C%20you%20can%20still%20use%20smart%20shopping%20strategies%20to%20find%20clothes%20that%20fit%20well.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECropped%20sweaters%20and%20jackets%2C%20ankle-length%20leggings%20and%20jeans%2C%20and%20%C2%BE-length%20or%20%26quot%3Bbracelet%26quot%3B%20sleeves%20are%20usually%20a%20safe%20bet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFAQs%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20you%20know%20if%20you're%20petite%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20general%20rule%2C%20many%20people%20who%20are%205-foot-4%20and%20under%20are%20considered%20petite.%20That%20said%2C%20petite%20doesn't%20%3Cem%3Ejust%20%3C%2Fem%3Emean%20short.%20Some%20people%20can%20get%20away%20with%20just%20hemming%20pants%20and%20jeans%2C%20but%20you'll%20know%20you%20need%20to%20buy%20petite%20clothing%20if%20tops%20also%20run%20too%20long%20in%20the%20torso%20and%20sleeves%2C%20rises%20are%20too%20high%2C%20dresses%20and%20outerwear%20tend%20to%20overwhelm%20your%20figure%2C%20and%20straps%20and%20shoulders%20often%20fall%20off.%20If%20you%20often%20find%20yourself%20rolling%20up%20or%20cuffing%20your%20sleeves%20and%20pants%2C%20that's%20another%20good%20sign%20that%20you%20could%20benefit%20from%20buying%20petite%20clothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKeep%20in%20mind%2C%20too%20that%20you%20can%20be%20any%20size%20and%20be%20petite%20%E2%80%94%20because%20petite%20isn't%20about%20your%20body%20size%2C%20but%20your%20body%20proportions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDoes%20petite%20sizing%20mean%20the%20garments%20run%20small%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EPetite%20sizing%20doesn't%20necessarily%20run%20smaller.%20So%2C%20if%20you%20always%20wore%20a%20medium%20in%20traditional%20clothing%2C%20you'll%20likely%20find%20that%20a%20medium%20petite%20fits%20perfectly.%20That%20said%2C%20this%20can%20vary%20a%20bit%20from%20brand%20to%20brand%2C%20so%20always%20check%20the%20size%20chart%20for%20more%20guidance%20on%20the%20specific%20item%20you're%20buying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20should%20petite%20clothing%20fit%20differently%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20petite%20clothing%2C%20you'll%20find%20that%20everything%20lines%20up%20better%20%E2%80%94%20seams%20hit%20right%20where%20they%20should%20on%20your%20shoulders%20and%20waist%2C%20and%20sleeves%20fall%20at%20the%20perfect%20spot%20on%20your%20wrist.%20With%20pants%2C%20there%20should%20be%20no%20bunching%20or%20sagging%20in%20the%20crotch%20or%20knees%2C%20and%20the%20length%20should%20graze%20your%20ankle%20(or%20lower%20calf%20for%20cropped%20styles)%20without%20having%20to%20be%20hemmed.%20You'll%20probably%20find%20that%20overall%2C%20petite%20clothing%20is%20just%20more%20flattering%20%E2%80%94%20dresses%2C%20skirts%2C%20sweaters%2C%20blouses%2C%20and%20jackets%20don't%20overwhelm%20your%20frame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-petite-clothing%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771539163000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6997788ba645d1188189a15b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%