ad%20introduced%20him%20to%20Epstein.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20unanswered%20questions%20remain%20about%20the%20relationship%20between%20Andrew%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20%E2%80%94%20formerly%20Prince%20Andrew%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%2C%20but%20the%20former%20royal%20once%20said%20they%20were%20introduced%20by%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaxwell%2C%20the%20British%20socialite%20who%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fghislaine-maxwell-sentenced-20-years-prison-sex-trafficking-jeffrey-epstein-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esentenced%20to%2020%20years%20in%20prison%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20sex-trafficking%20underage%20girls%20for%20Epstein%20after%20pleading%20not%20guilty%2C%20and%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20are%20understood%20to%20have%20enjoyed%20a%20close%20friendship%20in%20the%20'90s%20and%20early%202000s%2C%20when%20they%20were%20regularly%20spotted%20together%20on%20the%20New%20York%20and%20London%20social%20scenes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20sources%20who%20were%20interviewed%20for%20the%202022%20ITV%20documentary%20%26quot%3BGhislaine%2C%20Prince%20Andrew%20and%20the%20Paedophile%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fghislaine-maxwell-prince-andrew-intimate-relationship-former-buckingham-palace-officer-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20that%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20and%20Maxwell%20were%20so%20close%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Buckingham%20Palace%20staff%20believed%20they%20dated%20at%20one%20point%20in%20the%20early%20aughts.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20in%20the%20early%202000s%20that%20Epstein%20victim%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvirginia-roberts-sexual-assault-claims-prince-andrew-timeline-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVirginia%20Giuffre%20alleges%20Epstein%20and%20Maxwell%20made%20her%20sleep%20with%20the%20then-prince%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20multiple%20occasions%20when%20she%20was%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiuffre%2C%20who%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%20April%202025%2C%20sued%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20in%202021%20over%20allegations%20he%20sexually%20assaulted%20her%20at%20Maxwell's%20London%20home%2C%20at%20Epstein's%20New%20York%20home%2C%20and%20on%20Epstein's%20private%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMountbatten-Windsor%20has%20long%20denied%20the%20allegations%2C%20saying%20he%20doesn't%20recall%20ever%20meeting%20Giuffre.%20Still%2C%20in%202022%2C%20they%20reached%20a%20settlement%20for%20an%20undisclosed%20amount.%20He%20has%20also%20been%20stripped%20of%20his%20royal%20patronages%20and%20military%20and%20royal%20titles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20he%20was%20arrested%20on%20suspicion%20of%20misconduct%20in%20public%20office%20amid%20renewed%20scrutiny%20over%20his%20relationship%20with%20Epstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20long%20been%20tied%20to%20Epstein%20through%20his%20friendship%20with%20Maxwell.%20Here's%20a%20timeline%20of%20their%20friendship%20as%20documented%20in%20news%20reports%20and%20interviews%20over%20the%20years.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b9b3deea-4ba5-4a8e-882b-b184b3844a21%5C%22%3EMountbatten-Windsor%20met%20Maxwell%20when%20she%20was%20at%20university%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMountbatten-Windsor%20said%20in%20his%20infamous%20November%202019%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-50449339%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBBC%20Newsnight%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he'd%20known%20Maxwell%20since%20her%20university%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaxwell%20attended%20Oxford%20University%2C%20graduating%20in%201985%2C%20during%20which%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20was%20serving%20in%20the%20Royal%20Navy.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaxwell%20also%20came%20from%20a%20well-connected%20family.%20Her%20father%2C%20Robert%20Maxwell%2C%20was%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20Daily%20Mirror%20newspaper%20and%20a%20onetime%20member%20of%20Parliament%20before%20his%20death%20in%201991.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220f5ee4e2-6758-477a-8cbd-66449980392a%5C%22%3EThe%20pair%20were%20often%20spotted%20together%20in%20the%20late%20'90s%20and%20early%20aughts%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMaxwell%20and%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20seemed%20especially%20close%20in%20the%20late%201990s%20and%20early%202000s%2C%20when%20their%20outings%20on%20the%20New%20York%20and%20London%20social%20scene%20were%20widely%20covered%20in%20the%20press%2C%20and%20the%20friends%20were%20often%20pictured%20together.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFebruary%201999%3A%20Flight%20logs%20obtained%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-news%2Fprince-andrew-flew-paedophile-pal-5037951%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDaily%20Mirror%3C%2Fa%3E%20show%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20flew%20with%20Maxwell%20aboard%20Epstein's%20private%20jet%20to%20the%20financier's%20private%20Caribbean%20island%2C%20Little%20St.%20James.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELate%20summer%2Fearly%20autumn%201999%3A%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20hosts%20Maxwell%20and%20Epstein%20at%20Balmoral%2C%20according%20to%20a%20model%20who%20attended%20the%20getaway%20and%20later%20spoke%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-7369849%2FDuke-York-appalled-Epstein-sex-scandal-claims.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDaily%20Mail%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221309%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jeffrey%20Epstein%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61e73f287c6a20001842785a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22982%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EImages%20introduced%20at%20Maxwell's%20trial%20included%20a%20photograph%20of%20her%20and%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20relaxing%20at%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20Balmoral%2C%20Queen%20Elizabeth's%20royal%20residence%20in%20the%20Scottish%20highlands.%3Cp%3EUS%20Attorney's%20Office%20for%20the%20Southern%20District%20of%20New%20York%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFebruary%202000%3A%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20vacations%20at%20Mar-a-Lago%20with%20Maxwell%20before%20attending%20a%20fashion%20show%20in%20New%20York%2C%20according%20to%20a%202001%20article%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mintpressnews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2FANDREW_S-FIXER_SHE_S-THE-DAUGHTER-OF-ROBERT-MAXWELL-AND-1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Evening%20Standard.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EApril%202000%3A%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20makes%20another%20trip%20to%20New%20York%2C%20where%20he%20%26quot%3Bsocialized%20with%20Ghislaine%2C%26quot%3B%20The%20Evening%20Standard%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMay%2012%2C%202000%3A%20Flight%20logs%20again%20show%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20flying%20aboard%20Epstein's%20private%20jet%20from%20New%20Jersey%20to%20Palm%20Beach%2C%20Florida%2C%20with%20Maxwell%20also%20on%20board.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJune%2021%2C%202000%3A%20Epstein%20and%20Maxwell%20attend%20a%20party%20at%20Windsor%20Castle%2C%20partially%20in%20honor%20of%20the%20prince's%2040th%20birthday%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-49411215%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJune%2022%2C%202000%3A%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20and%20Maxwell%20are%20pictured%20attending%20the%20Royal%20Ascot.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221312%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Andrew%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20and%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell%20at%20the%20Royal%20Ascot%20in%20June%202000.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699730d1f8731049f3af6510%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221929%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndrew%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20and%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell%20at%20the%20Royal%20Ascot%20in%20June%202000.%3Cp%3ETim%20Graham%20Photo%20Library%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESeptember%202000%3A%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20and%20Maxwell%20are%20pictured%20together%20at%20the%20Wiltshire%20wedding%20of%20the%20prince's%20former%20girlfriend%2C%20Aurelia%20Cecil.%20Pictures%20show%20the%20two%20arriving%20at%20the%20wedding%20in%20the%20same%20car%2C%20the%20BBC%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOctober%2031%2C%202000%3A%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20and%20Maxwell%20were%20pictured%20together%20at%20Heidi%20Klum's%20Halloween%20party%20in%20Manhattan.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDecember%202000%3A%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20hosted%20Maxwell%20and%20Epstein%20at%20Sandringham%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bstraightforward%20shooting%20weekend%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20his%202019%20BBC%20Newsnight%20interview.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJanuary%202001%3A%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20takes%20a%20trip%20to%20Thailand%20with%20Maxwell%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mintpressnews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2FANDREW_S-FIXER_SHE_S-THE-DAUGHTER-OF-ROBERT-MAXWELL-AND-1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Evening%20Standard%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMarch%202001%3A%20Virginia%20Giuffre%20alleged%20that%20she%20met%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20for%20the%20first%20time%20at%20Maxwell's%20townhouse%2C%20in%20a%20meeting%20arranged%20by%20Maxwell%20and%20Epstein.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMaxwell%20and%20Epstein%20were%20believed%20to%20be%20dating%20at%20some%20point%20during%20this%20era.%20At%20Maxwell's%20child-sex-trafficking%20trial%20in%202021%2C%20Cimberly%20Espinosa%20testified%20that%20she%20worked%20at%20Epstein's%20company%20from%201996%20to%202002%2C%20largely%20as%20Maxwell's%20executive%20assistant.%20Espinosa%20said%20that%20when%20she%20first%20started%20at%20the%20company%2C%20she%20believed%20Epstein%20and%20Maxwell%20were%20dating%2C%20but%20she%20got%20the%20impression%20they%20broke%20up%20sometime%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%20of%20her%20employment%20at%20J.%20Epstein%20and%20Co.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bbe687db-9dc0-4457-91cf-f890a9d70b85%5C%22%3EA%20former%20Buckingham%20Palace%20royal%20protection%20officer%20says%20Maxwell%20visited%20so%20often%20that%20he%20suspected%20she%20and%20the%20prince%20were%20dating%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMountbatten-Windsor%20and%20Maxwell%20may%20have%20started%20dating%20around%202001%2C%20according%20to%20Paul%20Page%2C%20a%20former%20royal%20protection%20officer%20who%20spoke%20for%20the%20ITV%20documentary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPage%20said%20he%20first%20met%20Maxwell%20in%202001%2C%20and%20that%20Buckingham%20Palace%20staff%20suspected%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20and%20Maxwell%20had%20an%20%26quot%3Bintimate%20relationship%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20frequency%20of%20her%20visits.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20way%20she%20was%20allowed%20to%20enter%20and%20exit%20the%20palace%2C%20at%20will%2C%20we%20realized%20%E2%80%A6%20suspected%20that%20she%20may%20have%20had%20an%20intimate%20relationship%20with%20Prince%20Andrew%2C%26quot%3B%20Page%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20colleague%20of%20mine%20remembered%20her%20coming%20in%20four%20times%20in%20one%20day%20from%20the%20morning%20till%20the%20evening%20%E2%80%94%20she%20kept%20coming%20in%20and%20out%2C%20in%20and%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Froyal-family%2F2022%2F01%2F17%2Fprince-andrew-may-have-dated-ghislaine-maxwell-say-friends%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esource%20who%20spoke%20on%20the%20program%20was%20Euan%20Rellie%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20banker%20who%20said%20he%20also%20became%20friendly%20with%20Maxwell%20during%20university.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20the%20sense%20that%20Prince%20Andrew%20and%20Ghislaine%20had%20probably%20been%20girlfriend%20and%20boyfriend%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20Rellie%20said%20in%20the%20documentary%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Telegraph.%20%26quot%3BThey%20had%20an%20easy%20warmth%20around%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20the%20documentary's%20release%2C%20Prince%20Andrew's%20press%20office%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224efe5c32-d628-4b56-8138-faa796670e77%5C%22%3EYears%20later%2C%20Maxwell%20is%20behind%20bars%2C%20and%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20was%20arrested%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrew-mountbatten-windsor-arrested-suspicion-misconduct-public-office-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMountbatten-Windsor%20was%20arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20suspicion%20of%20misconduct%20in%20public%20office.%20He%20was%20released%20hours%20later%2C%20and%20police%20said%20an%20investigation%20is%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20following%20the%20release%20of%20documents%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fepstein-files-why-on-the-internet-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20Justice%20Department's%20Investigation%20into%20Epstein%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20UK's%20Thames%20Valley%20Police%20said%20it%20was%20looking%20into%20claims%20that%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20shared%20confidential%20trade%20reports%20with%20Epstein%20in%202010%2C%20when%20Mountbatten-Windsor%20was%20a%20trade%20envoy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20previously%20denied%20all%20allegations%20against%20him.%20In%20a%202019%20statement%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAt%20no%20stage%20during%20the%20limited%20time%20I%20spent%20with%20him%20did%20I%20see%2C%20witness%20or%20suspect%20any%20behaviour%20of%20the%20sort%20that%20subsequently%20led%20to%20his%20arrest%20and%20conviction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMountbatten-Windsor%20has%20not%20commented%20publicly%20on%20the%20recent%20allegations%20of%20misconduct%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20the%20arrest%20on%20Thursday%2C%20King%20Charles%2C%20Mountbatten-Windsor's%20brother%2C%20released%20a%20statement%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20law%20must%20take%20its%20course.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20own%20statement%2C%20the%20family%20of%20Virginia%20Giuffre%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20our%20broken%20hearts%20have%20been%20lifted%20by%20the%20news%20that%20no%20one%20is%20above%20the%20law%2C%20not%20even%20royalty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEditor's%20note%3A%20A%20version%20of%20this%20story%20was%20previously%20published%20in%20June%202022.%20It%20was%20updated%20in%20February%202026.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprince-andrew-ghislaine-maxwell-friendship-timeline-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771529093000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61e724867c6a2000184271fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprince-andrew-ghislaine-maxwell-friendship-timeline-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Andrew%20Mountbatten-Windsor%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20Thursday%2C%20previously%20said%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell%20introduced%20him%20to%20Jeffrey%20Epstein.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22acollman%40businessinsider.com%20(Ashley%20Collman%2CIsabella%20Zavarise)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprince-andrew-ghislaine-maxwell-friendship-timeline-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20crypto%20firm%20with%20ties%20to%20Trump%20will%20'tokenize'%20some%20of%20the%20president's%20real%20estate%20empire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22trump%20real%20estate%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69972697a645d1188189954e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222670%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EArtur%20Widak%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWorld%20Liberty%20Financial%20is%20set%20to%20tokenize%20loan%20revenue%20from%20a%20Trump%20Maldives%20hotel.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETrump's%20sons%20are%20listed%20among%20the%20co-founders%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tokenized%20offering%20will%20offer%20investors%20cash%20flows%20from%20the%20repayment%20of%20a%20construction%20loan.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWorld%20Liberty%20Financial%2C%20the%20crypto%20firm%20cofounded%20and%20partly%20run%20by%20the%20Trump%20family%2C%20will%20tokenize%20loan%20revenue%20interest%20from%20a%20new%20Trump%20International%20Hotel%20and%20Resort%20in%20the%20Maldives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftokenized-stock-equity-tokens-robinhood-vlad-tenev-crypto-blockchain-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETokenization%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20process%20of%20putting%20an%20asset%20on%20the%20blockchain%20to%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20crypto%20token%20that%20can%20be%20easily%20traded%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20a%20loan%20used%20to%20fund%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20hotel.%20Investors%20who%20buy%20tokenized%20pieces%20of%20the%20loan%20will%20be%20entitled%20to%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20interest%20payments%20made%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20WLF%20documents%2C%20DT%20Marks%20DEFI%20LLC%2C%20which%20is%20owned%20by%20the%20Trump%20family%2C%20reserves%20the%20right%20to%20receive%2075%25%20of%20the%20revenue%20generated%20from%20%24WFLI%20token%20sales%20after%20expenses.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20offering%20won't%20be%20available%20to%20everyone.%20Only%20accredited%20investors%2C%20or%20those%20with%20at%20least%20%241%20million%20in%20liquid%20assets%20and%20who%20make%20enough%20money%20per%20year%2C%20will%20be%20given%20access%20to%20the%20tokenized%20loan.%20The%20tokens%20will%20be%20offered%20in%20partnership%20with%20Securitize%2C%20Inc.%20and%20Dar%20Global%20PLC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20hotel%20in%20the%20Maldives%20is%20set%20to%20open%20in%202030%20and%20was%20announced%20in%20late%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20listed%20as%20%26quot%3BCofounder%20Emeritus%26quot%3B%20of%20World%20Liberty%20Financial%20on%20its%20website.%20His%20three%20sons%20%E2%80%94%20Don%20Jr.%2C%20Eric%2C%20and%20Baron%20%E2%80%94%20are%20listed%20as%20cofounders%2C%20as%20is%20Steve%20Witkoff%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20serving%20as%20United%20States%20special%20envoy%20to%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorld%20Liberty%20Financial's%20new%20tokenization%20offering%20is%20the%20Trump%20family's%20latest%20move%20in%20the%20crypto%20space.%20In%20January%202025%2C%20Trump%20launched%20%24Trump%20coin%2C%20a%20meme%20token%20that%20spiked%20to%20%2445%20shortly%20after%20launch%2C%20and%20currently%20trades%20at%20%243.40.%20According%20to%20Reuters%2C%20the%20coin%20made%20almost%20%24100%20million%20in%20fees%20in%20the%20first%20couple%20weeks%20after%20its%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWLF%20also%20sold%20a%2049%25%20stake%20in%20January%202025%20to%20an%20Emirati%20royal%20for%20%24500%20million%2C%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported.%20The%20firm%20launched%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-crypto-stablecoin-djt-stock-world-liberty-financial-usd1-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Establecoin%2C%20USD1%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20last%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrypto-crash-trump-family-trumpcoin-bitcoin-djt-btc-meme-coin-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETrump%20Media%20and%20Technology%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%20adopted%20a%20crypto%20treasury%20strategy%20last%20year%2C%20buying%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20bitcoin.%20According%20to%20a%20Bloomberg%20report%2C%20crypto%20had%20boosted%20the%20Trump%20family's%20net%20worth%20by%20%241.4%20billion%20as%20of%20January%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20token%20offering%20from%20WLF%20comes%20as%20crypto%20assets%20endure%20a%20brutal%20bear%20market%20as%20funds%20flee%20the%20space.%20Bitcoin's%20price%20is%20down%2045%25%20from%20October's%20high%2C%20while%20ethereum%20has%20fallen%2059%25%20since%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-liberty-financial-trump-crypto-firm-tokenize-real-estate-empire-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771529042000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699726b5f8731049f3af6352%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-liberty-financial-trump-crypto-firm-tokenize-real-estate-empire-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tokenization%20allows%20investors%20to%20own%20a%20share%20of%20a%20real-world%20asset%20%E2%80%94%20in%20this%20case%2C%20a%20loan%20funding%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20Trump%20property%20in%20the%20Maldives.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-liberty-financial-trump-crypto-firm-tokenize-real-estate-empire-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20says%20world%20has%2010%20days%20to%20see%20if%20Iran%20agrees%20deal%20or%20'bad%20things%20happen'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771529035000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F043b%2Flive%2Fff016940-0daa-11f1-9fe5-57999fe11004.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc86yjnw4x49o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20is%20surging%20forces%20to%20the%20Middle%20East%20amid%20negotiations%20with%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20over%20its%20nuclear%20programme.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A481%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc86yjnw4x49o%2