0to%20build%20a%20data%20center%20in%20Claremore%2C%20Oklahoma.%3Cp%3EOselote%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOklahoma%20residents%20attended%20a%20meeting%20to%20discuss%20a%20proposed%20data%20center%20in%20Claremore.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDuring%20the%20public%20comment%20portion%2C%20authorities%20arrested%20a%20man%20for%20trespassing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20man%20spoke%20for%20about%2030%20seconds%20over%20his%20allotted%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EApplause%20broke%20out%20during%20an%20Oklahoma%20man's%20speech%20at%20a%20city%20council%20meeting%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20discuss%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-center-development-true-cost-environmental-impact-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproposed%20data%20center%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20minute%20later%2C%20shouts%20of%20disbelief%20rang%20out%20across%20the%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDisgusting!%26quot%3B%20one%20woman%20shouted%20as%20Claremore%20Police%20Department%20officers%20handcuffed%20and%20escorted%20Daniel%20Blanchard%20out%20of%20the%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20said%20they%20arrested%20Blanchard%2C%20whose%20speech%20exceeded%20the%20three-minute%20time%20limit%2C%20for%20trespassing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20100%20people%2C%20including%20Blanchard%2C%20had%20gathered%20in%20a%20ballroom%20at%20Rogers%20State%20University%20in%20Claremore%20to%20voice%20their%20opinions%20about%20the%20large%20data%20center%20project.%20The%20developer%2C%20Beale%20Infrastructure%2C%20is%20proposing%20a%20campus%20in%20the%20Claremore%20Industrial%20Park%20that%20includes%20data%20centers%2C%20supporting%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20office%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlanchard%20was%20among%20the%20residents%20who%20opted%20to%20speak%20during%20the%20public%20comment%20portion%2C%20which%20limits%20each%20person%20to%20three%20minutes.%20In%20his%20speech%2C%20Blanchard%20spoke%20about%20what%20he%20considered%20compliance%20issues%20related%20to%20the%20potential%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Claremore%20Industrial%20Economic%20Development%20Authority%20has%20a%20fiduciary%20responsibility%20to%20the%20public%2C%20not%20to%20build%20infrastructure.%20And%20this%20act%20of%20overreach%20is%20putting%20the%20health%20and%20safety%20of%20members%20of%20this%20community%20at%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20driving%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-locations-us-map-ai-boom-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edata%20center%20construction%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20United%20States.%20While%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-data-center-expansion-is-hungry-for-workers-and-electricity-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompanies%20like%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20argue%20that%20building%20new%20data%20centers%20will%20reindustrialize%20the%20US%20economy%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20create%20jobs%2C%20residents%20of%20towns%20where%20developers%20are%20proposing%20new%20data%20centers%20worry%20about%20their%20impact%20on%20power%20grids%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-data-centers-are-deepening-the-water-crisis-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewater%20resources%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20pollution%2C%20and%20overall%20quality%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20investigation%20published%20in%20September%2C%20Business%20Insider%20reported%20that%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-locations-us-map-ai-boom-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1%2C200%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20already%20been%20built%20or%20were%20approved%20for%20construction%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20data%20center%20in%20Claremore%2C%20a%20suburban%20hub%20of%20Tulsa%20home%20to%20about%2020%2C000%20people%2C%20has%20divided%20the%20town.%20During%20the%20three-hour%20meeting%20on%20Tuesday%20evening%2C%20dozens%20of%20residents%20spoke%20both%20in%20favor%20and%20against%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlanchard%20exceeded%20his%20three%20minutes%20by%20about%2030%20seconds%20before%20police%20officers%20approached%20him.%20He%20gathered%20his%20notes%20and%20calmly%20followed%20the%20officers%20to%20the%20front%20of%20the%20hall%2C%20where%20town%20officials%20were%20sitting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20of%20the%20meeting%20posted%20by%20the%20town%20on%20its%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20Blanchard%20appears%20to%20hand%20his%20notes%20to%20a%20council%20member.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20police%20arrested%20Blanchard%2C%20placing%20him%20in%20handcuffs.%20The%20crowd%20hollered%20in%20shock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Claremore%20Police%20Department%20said%20officers%20aren't%20responsible%20for%20enforcing%20city%20council%20rules%20and%20only%20become%20involved%20in%20city%20council%20meetings%20when%20an%20official%20orders%20them%20to%20remove%20an%20individual.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20man's%20position%20on%20the%20issues%2C%20what%20he%20said%2C%20or%20his%20unwillingness%20to%20follow%20rules%20of%20the%20meeting%20played%20no%20part%20in%20the%20officer's%20decision%20to%20arrest%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20arrested%20for%20trespassing%20in%20compliance%20with%20the%20law%20and%20with%20the%20hope%20of%20restoring%20order%20to%20an%20important%20meeting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20local%20politician%20fighting%20the%20data%20center%20project%20posted%20to%20X%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20Blanchard%20has%20been%20released%20from%20jail.%20The%20next%20council%20meeting%20is%20scheduled%20for%20March%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-meeting-claremore-oklahoma-man-arrested-beale-infrastructure-ai-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insi