f.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fa39b%2Flive%2Fc6cf6130-0db4-11f1-a954-b3152d2d59e8.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcp8rke05kv4o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Blooks%20like%26quot%3B%20Hamas%20will%20disarm%2C%20even%20though%20there%20are%20signs%20the%20group%20is%20regrouping.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A40%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcp8rke05kv4o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20top%20options%20firm%20is%20hiring%20traders%20to%20bet%20on%20the%20weather%20and%20other%20'event-driven%20outcomes'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225968%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kalshi's%20website%20viewed%20through%20a%20magnifying%20glass.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69950e16f8731049f3af4ab9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223979%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKalshi's%20website%3Cp%3EThomas%20Fuller%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESusquehanna%20is%20looking%20to%20hire%20several%20pros%20to%20trade%20in%20the%20booming%20prediction%20markets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20roles%20will%20center%20on%20building%20real-time%20models%20to%20help%20inform%20bets%20on%20event-driven%20outcomes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPrediction%20sites%20like%20Polymarket%20and%20Kalshi%20have%20boomed%20in%20the%20last%20year.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPrediction%20markets%20are%20booming%2C%20and%20the%20hype%20is%20spreading%20beyond%20the%20retail%20crowd%20to%20major%20trading%20firms.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOptions-trading%20giant%20Susquehanna%20International%20Group%20is%20seeking%20to%20expand%20into%20the%20booming%20market%20where%20traders%20can%20bet%20on%20everything%20from%20Fed%20rate%20cuts%20to%20the%20likelihood%20of%20a%20snowstorm.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcareers.sig.com%2Fjob%2F10418%2FSenior-Trader-Prediction-Markets-Experienced-Hire%3Futm_campaign%3Dgoogle_jobs_apply%26utm_source%3Dgoogle_jobs_apply%26utm_medium%3Dorganic%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecareers%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20is%20looking%20to%20hire%20several%20prediction%20market%20traders.%20The%20roles%20will%20center%20on%20designing%20and%20implementing%20real-time%20models%20to%20assist%20with%20betting%20on%20the%20type%20of%20event-driven%20outcomes%20that%20made%20prediction%20markets%20popular%2C%20including%20what%20tomorrow's%20weather%20might%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrediction%20markets%20are%20relatively%20new%2C%20with%20their%20popularity%20exploding%20around%20the%20time%20of%20the%202024%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ideal%20candidate%20combines%20strong%20trading%20intuition%2C%20robust%20statistical%20and%20programming%20skills%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20translate%20ambiguous%20problems%20into%20structured%2C%20high-quality%20models%20that%20drive%20profitable%20decision-making%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcareers.sig.com%2Fjob%2F10418%2FSenior-Trader-Prediction-Markets-Experienced-Hire%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejob%20posting%3C%2Fa%3E%20reads.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWow.%20One%20of%20the%20biggest%20options%20trading%20firms%20in%20the%20world%20is%20hiring%20a%20Senior%20Trader%20for%20Prediction%20Markets.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ESusquehanna%20(SIG)%20is%20looking%20for%20someone%20to%20build%20real-time%20models%20for%20uncertain%2C%20event-driven%20outcomes%20(weather%2C%20probabilistic%20events%2C%20etc.)%2C%20turn%20those%20into%20fair%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FaGFw5Ih3rY%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FaGFw5Ih3rY%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Frank%20Chaparro%20(%40fintechfrank)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffintechfrank%2Fstatus%2F2023792563149328871%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2017%2C%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ESusquehanna%20has%20ventured%20into%20betting%20markets%20before.%20In%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquant-trading-susquehanna-sports-betting-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eit%20launched%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%2015-person%20sports%20betting%20team%20at%20its%20office%20in%20Dublin%2C%20and%20indicated%20plans%20to%20expand%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20not%20the%20first%20sign%20that%20major%20institutions%20are%20looking%20to%20get%20in%20on%20the%20action%20in%20prediction%20markets.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fgs-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fa%3E%20CEO%20David%20Solomon%20said%20during%20the%20bank's%20most%20recent%20earnings%20call%20that%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-prediction-markets-polymarket-kalshi-earnings-david-solomon-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexploring%20opportunities%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20space.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlex%20Taaffe%2C%20chief%20revenue%20officer%20at%20crypto%20market%20maker%20GSR%2C%20said%20he%20isn't%20surprised%20by%20Susquehanna's%20decision%20to%20expand%20into%20prediction%20markets%20now.%20He%20sees%20this%20as%20a%20watershed%20moment%20and%20predicts%20further%20adoption%20by%20big%20Wall%20Street%20players.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20time%2C%20prediction%20markets%20will%20increasingly%20serve%20as%20benchmarks%20and%20data%20points%20that%20investors%20can%20use%20to%20hedge%20risk%2C%20express%20macro%20views%2C%20and%20complement%20existing%20instruments%20across%20rates%2C%20equities%2C%20and%20other%20asset%20classes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarek%20Sandrik%2C%20partner%20at%20the%20blockchain-focused%20venture%20capital%20firm%20RockawayX%2C%20said%20Susquehanna's%20move%20shows%20that%20prediction%20markets%20are%20maturing%2C%20evolving%20from%20a%20highly%20speculative%20vehicle%20into%20a%20real-time%20sentiment%20tool%20for%20investors%20to%20gauge%20key%20event%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Reserve%20this%20week%20said%20in%20a%20report%20that%20prediction%20markets%20platform%20Kalshi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-reserve-study-kalshi-economic-forecasting-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecan%20be%20useful%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20forecasting%20economic%20events.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESandrik%20also%20thinks%20that%20rising%20interest%20from%20Wall%20Street%20could%20help%20address%20certain%20problems%20that%20have%20been%20a%20hindrance%20to%20the%20burgeoning%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20prediction%20markets%20struggle%20with%20weak%20liquidity%20and%20murky%20regulatory%20frameworks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BInstitutional%20participation%20should%20address%20both%20challenges%20and%20contribute%20to%20a%20better%20user%20experience%20and%20accelerated%20growth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESusquehanna%20could%20not%20be%20reached%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprediction-markets-susquehanna-traders-options-betting-kalshi-wall-street-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771526563000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69975972a645d11881899d8e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprediction-markets-susquehanna-traders-options-betting-kalshi-wall-street-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%2