20stars%20weren't%20exactly%20aligning%20in%20my%20favor.%20Friends%20either%20already%20had%20their%20schedules%20booked%2C%20were%20tied%20up%20with%20other%20responsibilities%2C%20or%20just%20didn't%20respond%20when%20I%20asked%20if%20they%20were%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20understand%20life%20is%20busy%2C%20but%20I%20did%20feel%20a%20bit%20sad%20that%20no%20one%20showed%20a%20lot%20of%20interest%20in%20celebrating%20with%20me.%20Still%2C%20one%20thing%20I'm%20trying%20to%20learn%20as%20I%20get%20older%20is%20that%20I%20can't%20press%20pause%20on%20my%20happiness%20just%20because%20other%20people%20aren't%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20I%20booked%20my%20very%20first%20solo%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-people-like-all-inclusive-resorts-first-stay-mexico-skeptical-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrip%20to%20an%20all-inclusive%20resort%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Canc%C3%BAn%2C%20and%20it%20ended%20up%20being%20exactly%20what%20I%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2267599b71-02d8-4b2b-b8e6-59e93f02c2f8%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20day%20felt%20a%20little%20uncomfortable%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221582%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20lazy%20river%20on%20a%20sunny%20day%20at%20a%20Canc%C3%BAn%20resort.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6994be29e1ba468a96ac2d4f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221164%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3Ecaptiontk%3Cp%3ESukhman%20Rekhi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20I%20landed%20in%20Mexico%2C%20it%20hit%20me%20that%20it%20was%20my%20first%20time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdigital-nomad-lessons-learned-tips-things-to-know-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etraveling%20outside%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%2024%20years%20%E2%80%94%20and%20if%20you've%20done%20the%20math%2C%20that%20last%20time%20was%20when%20I%20was%205%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimple%20things%20like%20g