ip%20means%20you%20often%20have%20to%20take%20into%20consideration%20several%20other%20people's%20opinions%20about%20what%20to%20eat%2C%20where%20to%20go%2C%20when%20to%20rest%20%E2%80%A6%20the%20list%20goes%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nice%20thing%20about%20being%20at%20an%20all-inclusive%20alone%2C%20though%2C%20was%20that%20my%20trip%20was%20already%20somewhat%20planned.%20I%20just%20got%20to%20sit%20back%20and%20handpick%20the%20things%20I%20actually%20wanted%20to%20do%20%E2%80%94%20without%20any%20compromises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESleep%20in%20until%20noon%3F%20Sure.%20Order%20room%20service%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%3F%20Go%20for%20it.%20Attend%20the%20morning%20sip-and-paint%20class%3F%20Check.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20wanted%20to%20spontaneously%20take%20a%20dip%20in%20the%20ocean%20even%20after%20straightening%20my%20hair%20and%20putting%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsephora-beauty-products-full-face-makeup-recommendations-from-employee-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efull%20face%20of%20makeup%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20could%2C%20and%20no%20one%20would%20stop%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20all%20of%20these%20absolutely%20guilt-free%2C%20because%20I%20wasn't%20responsible%20for%20anyone%20else%20and%20nobody%20was%20waiting%20on%20me%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223489af7e-b799-405e-8bb6-b9676f2a4027%5C%22%3EI%20got%20to%20catch%20up%20on%20so%20many%20things%20I%20was%20neglecting%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221550%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20quiet%20beach%20in%20Canc%C3%BAn%2C%20Mexico.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6994bb32e1ba468a96ac2d02%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221148%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOn%20my%20trip%2C%20I%20realized%20I'd%20been%20neglecting%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20needs.%3Cp%3ESukhman%20Rekhi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20on%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsid