D%5C%2230b2bd8f-1a9d-442d-b1e5-bd371a21cabf%5C%22%3ENetflix%20versus%20Paramount%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20has%20been%20on%20a%20charm%20campaign%20to%20convince%20the%20president%20and%20Hollywood%20that%20it%20would%20be%20a%20better%20buyer%20of%20Warner%20Bros.%20than%20rival%20bidder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavid-ellison-paramount-new-wbd-bid-warner-bros-netflix-regulatory-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EParamount%20Skydance%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20key%20part%20of%20Netflix's%20pitch%20is%20that%20it%20would%20cut%20fewer%20jobs%20than%20Paramount.%20Paramount%20has%20said%20it's%20planning%20to%20create%20%246%20billion%20in%20so-called%20synergies%2C%20which%20would%20likely%20include%20layoffs%2C%20while%20Netflix%20has%20told%20investors%20it's%20aiming%20for%20%242%20billion%20to%20%243%20billion%20in%20cost%20cuts%2C%20in%20part%20by%20saving%20money%20on%20licensing%20programming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWBD's%20board%20of%20directors%20seems%20sympathetic%20to%20Netflix's%20argument.%20The%20board%20warned%20shareholders%20that%20if%20it%20accepted%20Paramount's%20offer%2C%20there%20could%20be%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwbd-warns-of-employee-exodus-paramount-skydance-david-ellison-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexodus%20of%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%20seeking%20to%20avoid%20layoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAntitrust%20analysis%20often%20focuses%20on%20how%20strong%20a%20company%20is%20relative%20to%20its%20competitors%20and%20how%20the%20market%20power%20it%20could%20wield%20over%20consumers.%20Regulators%20also%20look%20at%20how%20a%20merger%20or%20acquisition%20would%20impact%20the%20production%20side%2C%20which%20in%20this%20case%20would%20be%20how%20many%20studios%20are%20competing%20to%20buy%20new%20movies%20or%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParamount%20has%20argued%20that%20Netflix%2C%20the%20largest%20paid%20streaming%20service%20with%20over%20325%20million%20subscrib