22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-is-cool-explained-why-target-competitor-clothes-fashion-prices-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estylish%20new%20outfits%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20has%20been%20the%20case%20for%20several%20quarters%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20fiscal%20year%2C%20Walmart's%20overall%20sales%20grew%204.7%25%20to%20%24713.2%20billion%2C%20with%20e-commerce%20increasing%20by%20nearly%2025%25%20to%20top%20%24150%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20Walmart's%20growth%2C%20e-commerce%20giant%20Amazon%20dethroned%20it%20as%20the%20world's%20largest%20company%20by%20revenue%20last%20year%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-report-q4-earnings-call-amzn-stock-live-updates-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24716.9%20billion%20in%20revenue%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20stock%20dipped%20immediately%20after%20the%20earnings%20report%20but%20recovered%20during%20trading%20on%20Thursday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Walmart's%20progress%20in%20e-commerce%20could%20give%20Amazon%20a%20run%20for%20its%20money%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20physical%20proximity%20to%2095%25%20of%20US%20households.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStores%20are%20a%20huge%20part%20of%20the%20solution%20to%20deliver%20the%20customer%20experiences%20that%20the%20customers%20are%20looking%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-shuffles-top-leadership-team-as-ai-rapidly-reshapes-retail-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECEO%20John%20Furner%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20on%20the%20call.%20%26quot%3BHaving%20the%20US%20with%205%2C200%20locations%20between%20Walmart%20and%20Sam's%2C%20where%20inventory%20is%20forward-deployed%2C%20is%20really%20helpful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%2C%20for%20its%20part%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-fast-delivery-with-new-record-speed-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworking%20hard%20to%20counter%3C%2Fa%3E%20Walmart's%20dominant%20physical%20presence%2C%20which%20so%20far%20has%20given%20it%20an%20edge%20in%20delivering%20items%20like%20groceries%20and%20everyday%20essentials%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwill-amazon-walmart-30-minute-delivery-pay-off-debate-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein%20an%20hour%20or%20less%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224802d097-1c00-45b4-a662-30d3aff505af%5C%22%3EWalmart%20delivers%20the%20grocery%20aisle%20and%20the%20fashion%20catwalk%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20fresh%20food%20delivery%20that's%20helping%20Walmart%20reach%20new%20shoppers.%20Rainey%20said%20shoppers%20are%20using%20some%20of%20the%20savings%20from%20groceries%20to%20try%20new%20items%20from%20other%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%20convenience%2C%26quot%3B%20Rainey%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'd%20argue%20fashion%20is%20not%20really%20a%20convenience%20item.%20It%20shows%20that%20our%20broader%20assortment%20is%20appealing%20to%20a%20much%20larger%20customer%20base.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFashion%20not%20only%20led%20sales%20growth%20in%20general%20merchandise%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Rainey%20said%2C%20but%20on-trend%20styles%20are%20also%20helping%20draw%20in%20more%20of%20these%20high-income%20households%2C%20who%20wind%20up%20sticking%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20coming%20to%20Walmart%2C%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20some%20of%20them%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20and%20they're%20enjoying%20an%20experience%20that%20makes%20them%20want%20to%20come%20back%20these%20platforms%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlobalData%20retail%20analyst%20Neil%20Saunders%20said%20his%20firm's%20data%20also%20shows%20wealthy%20households%20increasingly%20choosing%20Walmart%20for%20more%20than%20groceries%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20expanded%20assortment%20and%20in-store%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20still%20too%20soon%20to%20see%20the%20impact%20of%20Walmart's%20recent%20AI%20partnerships%