0360%20mobile%20medical%20units%2C%20and%20172%20ambulances%20dispatched%20statewide%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20tells%20another%20story%20of%20a%20rescue%20where%20a%20little%20girl%20began%20crying%20as%20she%2C%20along%20with%20her%20family%2C%20was%20taken%20away%20to%20the%20relief%20camp%20in%20the%20rescue%20boat.%20She%20watched%20her%20house%2C%20the%20one%20that%20her%20father%20had%20taken%20a%20loan%20for%20and%20put%20his%20life%20savings%20into%20building%2C%20crumble%20to%20pieces%2C%20washed%20away%20brick%20by%20brick.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20her%20father%20consoled%20her%2C%20%E2%80%98Houses%20can%20be%20rebuilt.%20At%20least%20we%20are%20alive.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348884%2Fsenior-citizens-healthcare-boat-clinic-in-sundarbans-shis-foundation-abdul-wohab-sabitri-pal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThese%20stories%20reveal%20the%20unbreakable%20spirit%20of%20the%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Harmeet%20points%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%E2%80%99s%20going%20to%20take%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20time%20for%20the%20farmers%20to%20tide%20through%20the%20losses.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20animals%20are%20drowning%20and%20dying%3B%20this%20is%20leading%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20infections.%20We%20have%20our%20doctors%20across%20medical%20centres%20and%20relief%20camps%2C%20but%20the%20number%20of%20cases%20of%20waterborne%20diseases%2C%20skin%20infections%2C%20and%20diseases%20caused%20by%20mosquito%20bites%20is%20on%20the%20rise.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20losses%2C%20he%20says%20they%20will%20only%20be%20able%20to%20assess%20this%20once%20the%20flood%20waters%20ebb.%20However%2C%20the%20distress%20will%20continue%20for%20farmers%20like%20Mohan%20who%20do%20not%20have%20a%20home%20to%20go%20back%20to.%20It%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20the%20present%20that%20keeps%