20into%20smoothies%20or%20chutneys.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUse%20instead%20of%20coriander%20for%20a%20fresh%20garnish.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFour%20label-check%20rules%20for%20packaged%20foods%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELook%20at%20the%20first%203%20ingredients.%20If%20sugar%2C%20refined%20flour%2C%20or%20palm%20oil%20lead%20the%20list%2C%20skip%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EChoose%20products%20with%20less%20than%205%20g%20of%20sugar%20per%20serving.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPrefer%20snacks%20with%20whole%20grains%2C%20nuts%2C%20or%20seeds%20listed%20upfront.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAvoid%20items%20with%20too%20many%20unpronounceable%20additives%3B%20simple%20is%20better.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20handful%20of%20microgreens%20on%20a%20sandwich%20to%20a%20weekly%20batch%20of%20%3Cem%3Eragi%20laddoos%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20small%20steps%20can%20make%20a%20big%20difference.%20For%20India%2C%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20nutrition%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20reconnecting%20with%20roots%2C%20celebrating%20resilience%2C%20and%20giving%20our%20children%20the%20tools%20to%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757065097000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fmicrogreens_11zon-1756194438.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496778%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parents%20across%20India%20are%20rethinking%20school%20tiffins%20by%20replacing%20packaged%20snacks%20with%20nutrient-rich%20millets%20and%20microgreens.%20Easy%20to%20grow%20and%20cook%2C%20these%20superfoods%20boost%20children%E2%80%99s%20focus%2C%20growth%2C%20and%20immunity%20%E2%80%94%20making%20them%20fun%2C%20affordable%2C%20and%20practical%20lunchbox%20staples.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Srimoyee%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496778%2Fmillets-microgreens