20beetroot%20is%20edible%2C%20it%20offers%20both%20nutritional%20and%20artistic%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Indigo%20%E2%80%93%20Blue%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndigo%20is%20a%20traditional%20dye%20plant%20that%20has%20been%20used%20for%20centuries%2C%20particularly%20for%20textile%20colouring.%20While%20a%20little%20more%20demanding%20to%20grow%2C%20it%20flourishes%20in%20warm%20climates%20with%20well-drained%20soil%20and%20full%20sunlight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20extract%20the%20colour%2C%20the%20leaves%20are%20soaked%20in%20water%20and%20fermented%2C%20triggering%20a%20chemical%20reaction%20that%20releases%20a%20strong%20blue%20pigment.%20This%20process%20can%20be%20a%20fascinating%20natural%20science%20experiment%20for%20older%20children.%20Indigo%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20few%20reliable%20natural%20sources%20of%20true%20blue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20Spinach%20%E2%80%93%20Green%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpinach%20is%20a%20fast-growing%20leafy%20vegetable%20that%20thrives%20in%20cool%20to%20moderate%20temperatures%20and%20prefers%20partial%20shade.%20The%20leaves%20can%20be%20dried%20and%20crushed%20to%20make%20a%20gentle%20green%20powder%2C%20or%20juiced%20and%20mixed%20with%20flour%20to%20create%20a%20smoother%20texture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-26T192438.011_11zon-1756216499.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20leaves%20of%20a%20spinach%20plant%20can%20be%20dried%20and%20crushed%20to%20make%20a%20gentle%20green%20powder%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Gardener's%20Path%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-